00400 int 
00401 VanillaSearchReplyPacket::addMatch( const SearchMatch* theMatch,
00402                                     bool increaseCount)
00403 {
00404    mc2dbg4 << "addMatch start" << endl;
00405    int position = readLong( REPLY_HEADER_SIZE+4 );
00406    position += SEARCH_REPLY_HEADER_SIZE +4; // +4 for the emptyHack
00407 
00408    if (position < PACKET_FULL_LIMIT || !increaseCount) {
00409       // If not increaseCount then match if part of other match -> add it
00410 
00411       if ( increaseCount ) {
00412          incNumberOfMatches();
00413       }
00414       theMatch->save(this, position);
00415       updateSize(position);
00416    } else {
00417       mc2dbg8 << "Packet full!!!" << endl;
00418       position = -1;
00419    }
00420    return (position);
00421 }
